{
  "stem": "628.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's so good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They stopped the van.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The two gestapo got out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, my sister, she was kind of a-- suddenly, one of the gestapo must have said, I'll come-- must have said I'd come, that-- that's-- and-- we go-- go back to our home again.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Put the luggage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Until-- ba, da, da, then-- then-- then this is beginning January '43.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was only postponed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She wanted to go back to her home-- run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wanted to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life, at that moment, it was already-- OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But until March, '43, then it happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they came again-- into the van, into the [NON-ENGLISH] deportation place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All Jewish people came there to be deported.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't tell you how many-- must have been at least-- oh, at least, 10,000, 20,000, 30,000 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- we were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there-- there was school, [NON-ENGLISH] School.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They emptied these schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- I remember we-- then already we had to sleep on the-- on the floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandmother slept there, grandfather there, and I there, and my sister also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we were there a few days, then the war happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then one of-- they were all Jewish people who helped the deportation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had to do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some-- some schools, even directors from Jewish schools, gave away their addresses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's known.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They came up to my sister, and up to my grandmother, later on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they said, your grandchild, Gisa, we have to take away straight away-- to send her straight away to Birkenau-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They said-- I don't know if they said Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
